{"image_id": "TSN_2010_page_52", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "52", "bbox": [627.0, 1583.7, 654.1, 1611.4]}, {"text": "The objective of our undesignated interest rate swap is to manage interest rate risk exposure on a floating-rate bond. Our interest rate", "bbox": [75.0, 75.5, 1187.4, 98.6]}, {"text": "swap agreement effectively modifies our exposure to interest rate risk by converting a portion of the floating-rate bond to a fixed rate", "bbox": [75.0, 99.5, 1190.4, 122.6]}, {"text": "basis for the first five years, thus reducing the impact of the interest-rate changes on future interest expense. This interest rate swap", "bbox": [75.0, 123.4, 1171.9, 146.5]}, {"text": "does not qualify for hedge treatment due to differences in the underlying bond and swap contract interest-rate indices.", "bbox": [75.0, 147.4, 1061.6, 170.5]}, {"text": "We had the following aggregate outstanding notionals related to our undesignated positions:", "bbox": [75.0, 195.3, 820.7, 218.4]}, {"text": "Metric", "bbox": [552.0, 244.3, 612.6, 267.4]}, {"text": "October 2, 2010", "bbox": [735.2, 244.3, 875.1, 267.4]}, {"text": "October 3, 2009", "bbox": [997.7, 244.3, 1137.6, 267.4]}, {"text": "Commodity:", "bbox": [75.0, 269.3, 185.6, 292.4]}, {"text": "Corn", "bbox": [93.8, 293.3, 140.6, 316.4]}, {"text": "Bushels", "bbox": [541.5, 293.3, 612.8, 316.4]}, {"text": "38 million", "bbox": [783.8, 293.3, 875.3, 316.4]}, {"text": "11 million", "bbox": [1046.3, 293.3, 1137.7, 316.4]}, {"text": "Soy meal", "bbox": [93.8, 317.2, 177.0, 340.3]}, {"text": "Tons", "bbox": [565.9, 317.2, 612.8, 340.3]}, {"text": "367,000", "bbox": [802.2, 317.2, 875.2, 340.3]}, {"text": "73,000", "bbox": [1075.2, 317.2, 1137.7, 340.3]}, {"text": "Live Cattle", "bbox": [93.7, 341.2, 197.4, 364.3]}, {"text": "Pounds", "bbox": [546.2, 341.2, 612.8, 364.3]}, {"text": "73 million", "bbox": [783.8, 341.2, 875.4, 364.3]}, {"text": "82 million", "bbox": [1046.4, 341.2, 1138.0, 364.3]}, {"text": "Lean Hogs", "bbox": [93.8, 365.0, 189.8, 388.1]}, {"text": "Pounds", "bbox": [546.1, 365.0, 612.7, 388.1]}, {"text": "134 million", "bbox": [773.4, 365.0, 875.2, 388.1]}, {"text": "11 million", "bbox": [1046.3, 365.0, 1137.7, 388.1]}, {"text": "Natural Gas", "bbox": [93.8, 389.0, 198.9, 412.1]}, {"text": "British thermal units", "bbox": [436.1, 389.0, 612.4, 412.1]}, {"text": "450 billion", "bbox": [778.8, 389.0, 875.0, 412.1]}, {"text": "850 billion", "bbox": [1041.4, 389.0, 1137.6, 412.1]}, {"text": "Foreign Currency", "bbox": [75.0, 413.0, 227.8, 436.1]}, {"text": "United States dollars", "bbox": [434.0, 413.0, 612.7, 436.1]}, {"text": "$146 million", "bbox": [763.0, 413.0, 875.3, 436.1]}, {"text": "$124 million", "bbox": [1025.5, 413.0, 1137.8, 436.1]}, {"text": "Interest Rate", "bbox": [75.0, 436.9, 186.1, 460.0]}, {"text": "Average monthly notional debt", "bbox": [347.7, 436.9, 612.8, 460.0]}, {"text": "$53 million", "bbox": [773.5, 436.9, 875.3, 460.0]}, {"text": "$64 million", "bbox": [1036.0, 436.9, 1137.8, 460.0]}, {"text": "Included in our undesignated positions are certain commodity grain positions (which do not qualify for hedge treatment) we enter into", "bbox": [75.0, 485.9, 1198.5, 509.0]}, {"text": "to manage the risk of costs associated with forward sales to certain customers for which sales prices are determined under cost-plus", "bbox": [75.0, 509.9, 1174.7, 533.0]}, {"text": "arrangements. These unrealized positions totaled gains of $2 million and losses of $17 million at October 2, 2010, and October 3,", "bbox": [75.0, 533.8, 1158.8, 556.9]}, {"text": "2009, respectively. When these positions are liquidated, we expect any realized gains or losses will be reflected in the prices of the", "bbox": [75.0, 557.8, 1169.1, 580.9]}, {"text": "poultry products sold. Since these derivative positions did not qualify for hedge treatment, they initially created volatility in our", "bbox": [75.0, 581.8, 1143.6, 604.9]}, {"text": "earnings associated with changes in fair value. However, once the positions were liquidated and included in the sales price to the", "bbox": [75.0, 605.7, 1153.0, 628.8]}, {"text": "customer, there was ultimately no earnings impact as any previous fair value gains or losses were included in the prices of the poultry", "bbox": [75.0, 629.6, 1193.8, 652.8]}, {"text": "products.", "bbox": [75.0, 653.6, 157.2, 676.8]}, {"text": "The following table sets forth the pretax impact of the undesignated derivative instruments on the Consolidated Statements of Income", "bbox": [75.0, 701.5, 1194.5, 724.6]}, {"text": "(in millions):", "bbox": [75.0, 725.5, 189.6, 748.6]}, {"text": "Consolidated", "bbox": [644.8, 773.4, 760.0, 796.5]}, {"text": "Gain/(Loss)", "bbox": [939.2, 773.4, 1043.9, 796.5]}, {"text": "Statements of Income", "bbox": [573.1, 797.4, 760.0, 820.5]}, {"text": "Recognized", "bbox": [940.4, 797.4, 1044.1, 820.5]}, {"text": "Classification", "bbox": [640.3, 821.3, 759.9, 844.4]}, {"text": "in Earnings", "bbox": [943.2, 821.3, 1044.0, 844.4]}, {"text": "2010", "bbox": [834.8, 846.3, 881.6, 869.4]}, {"text": "2009", "bbox": [912.9, 846.3, 959.7, 869.4]}, {"text": "2008", "bbox": [997.1, 846.3, 1044.0, 869.4]}, {"text": "Derivatives not designated", "bbox": [75.0, 871.3, 302.4, 894.4]}, {"text": "as hedging instruments:", "bbox": [75.0, 895.3, 278.1, 918.4]}, {"text": "Commodity contracts", "bbox": [103.1, 919.2, 288.3, 942.3]}, {"text": "Sales", "bbox": [710.8, 919.2, 760.0, 942.3]}, {"text": "$27", "bbox": [845.1, 919.2, 881.6, 942.3]}, {"text": "$(34)", "bbox": [909.4, 919.2, 959.7, 942.3]}, {"text": "$(12)", "bbox": [993.6, 919.2, 1044.0, 942.3]}, {"text": "Commodity contracts", "bbox": [103.1, 943.2, 288.2, 966.3]}, {"text": "Cost of Sales", "bbox": [644.8, 943.2, 760.1, 966.3]}, {"text": "(20)", "bbox": [841.7, 943.2, 881.7, 966.3]}, {"text": "(151)", "bbox": [909.4, 943.2, 959.8, 966.3]}, {"text": "259", "bbox": [1007.5, 943.2, 1044.0, 966.3]}, {"text": "Foreign exchange contracts", "bbox": [103.1, 967.